  m_Name: Do you read any other comics
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  allLines:
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Do you read any other comics? Like, other than the ones we are apparently
      not allowed to talk about?
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "I do, I like action and fantasy. I just started reading Indestructable
      and I\u2019ve been enjoying it a lot.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Oh yeah, that\u2019s a good one. Did you watch the adaptation?\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "No, I always like reading the original comics first. Although I think
      I\u2019m almost caught up with the series, wanna rewatch it with me when I\u2019m
      done?\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'I have a TV that covers the entire wall. Wanna do it at mine?

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Sure! It\u2019s a date.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Fuck yeah.

      

'
